And she says...

01:13.247 --> 01:16.076
[AUDIENCE LAUGHING]

01:16.076 --> 01:18.469
[AUDIENCE APPLAUDING]

01:18.469 --> 01:19.862
Keep smiling,

01:19.862 --> 01:21.385
the sun might
come out tomorrow,

01:21.385 --> 01:23.126
but I'm here all week.
Good night!

01:23.126 --> 01:26.434
[UP-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYING]

01:26.434 --> 01:28.566
Y'all give it up
one more time

01:28.566 --> 01:30.960
for the brightest comedian
in town,

01:30.960 --> 01:33.049
Mr. Sunshine, everybody,
Mr. Sunshine.

01:33.049 --> 01:35.225
Remember our
drink specials tonight.

01:35.225 --> 01:38.185
It's one dollar off
all top shelf liquor,

01:38.185 --> 01:42.450
and after midnight,
all draft beers are two for one.

01:42.450 --> 01:44.713
And don't forget
that every Tuesday

01:44.713 --> 01:48.499
we support the best
in local comedy, right here,

01:48.499 --> 01:50.936
at the Last Laugh
Comedy Club.

01:52.721 --> 01:54.940
Yeah. Aah...

01:58.248 --> 02:00.337
Hey, buddy, you're performing
tonight, right?

02:00.337 --> 02:01.860
