02:55.436 --> 02:58.395
I couldn't remember
one goddamn bit,

02:58.395 --> 03:00.919
just stood there,
like an asshole,

03:00.919 --> 03:04.880
like a real fucking asshole.

03:04.880 --> 03:07.274
Still, there's nothing like
that first time on stage,

03:07.274 --> 03:08.492
you know what I mean?

03:13.062 --> 03:15.238
Hm.

03:15.238 --> 03:17.327
A real fucking asshole.

03:17.327 --> 03:19.068
We gonna play a few songs,

03:19.068 --> 03:21.375
and give everybody a chance
to freshen up their drink,

03:21.375 --> 03:24.029
until the next comedian
is ready to hit the stage.

03:24.029 --> 03:25.988
Uh, be careful there,
buddy, be careful.

03:25.988 --> 03:28.077
Uh, you can go on in,
ain't no cover tonight.

03:28.077 --> 03:29.383
I'm performing.

03:29.383 --> 03:30.949
Oh, okay.

03:30.949 --> 03:33.561
Ah, is that you?
That's me.

03:33.561 --> 03:36.390
Well, I sure hope you're funnier
than you are punctual.

03:36.390 --> 03:38.914
Next time, try to get here
before we close it up, you dig?

03:38.914 --> 03:40.437
There won't be
a next time.

03:40.437 --> 03:42.222
Aw, man.

03:42.222 --> 03:43.919
Loosen up, brother.
Loosen up, man.

03:43.919 --> 03:45.703
Look, I'm Randall.

03:45.703 --> 03:47.270
I own the joint.

03:47.270 --> 03:50.665
[CHUCKLES]
Finally got that itch, huh?

03:50.665 --> 03:52.144
Well, listen,

03:52.144 --> 03:54.364
