another round.

05:59.141 --> 06:00.316
This guy's
beyond the fringe.

06:00.316 --> 06:02.840
So I went looking
for another job,

06:02.840 --> 06:06.322
something new, something,
uh, different,

06:06.322 --> 06:09.281
but I realized that I lacked
the skills necessary

06:09.281 --> 06:11.327
