07:16.436 --> 07:18.786
How are your kids doing?"
Uh...

07:18.786 --> 07:20.178
"What's new at work?"

07:20.178 --> 07:22.398
Et cetera, et cetera,
et cetera.

07:22.398 --> 07:23.878
You understand
what I'm saying?

07:23.878 --> 07:25.923
Yeah, I think so.

07:25.923 --> 07:28.578
Every customer that walks
through that door

07:28.578 --> 07:30.885
is like another member
of the Miller's family.

07:30.885 --> 07:32.016
That's a pretty big family.

07:32.016 --> 07:34.497
[CHUCKLES]
I opened this restaurant

07:34.497 --> 07:37.021
with the idea
that great home-cooked meals,

07:37.021 --> 07:40.982
at a reasonable price,
and world-class customer service

07:40.982 --> 07:42.984
would never go out of style.

07:42.984 --> 07:46.030
And I am proud to say
that after 19 years in business,

07:46.030 --> 07:47.945
