cinnamon-flavored sticky buns

08:31.859 --> 08:33.469
for your family to enjoy.

08:33.469 --> 08:35.340
But be careful,
don't fill up

08:35.340 --> 08:37.168
before your home-cooked meal
has arrived.

08:37.168 --> 08:39.082
And when you're finished,
every customer--

08:39.082 --> 08:40.780
