a sticky bun

08:40.780 --> 08:42.609
to enjoy for a late night snack,
as a reminder

08:42.609 --> 08:44.959
of the Miller's
family restaurant experience.

08:44.959 --> 08:46.787
[CHUCKLES]
Can I go?

08:46.787 --> 08:48.049
Yes, thank you, darling.

08:48.049 --> 08:49.137
A pleasure.

08:49.137 --> 08:50.094
Yeah.

08:52.880 --> 08:54.142
Dig in.

08:59.669 --> 09:02.454
[CHUCKLES]
