No.

14:19.119 --> 14:21.077
Madison--
No.

14:21.991 --> 14:23.123
Let's go.

14:25.299 --> 14:27.040
Sit down!

14:27.040 --> 14:28.650
Don't worry.

14:28.650 --> 14:29.956
We're not coming back.

14:29.956 --> 14:31.958
So you can take your school

14:31.958 --> 14:33.829
