At Miller's
Family Restaurant,

17:12.074 --> 17:14.032
we're ready to serve you,
just like we've been

17:14.032 --> 17:16.470
serving our own family
for generations.

17:16.470 --> 17:18.602
At Miller's, we're dedicated
to serving you

17:18.602 --> 17:21.518
great home-cooked meals,
at affordable prices,

17:21.518 --> 17:23.954
with world-class
customer service.

17:23.954 --> 17:27.002
Whether you choose our famous
meatloaf and mashed potatoes,

17:27.002 --> 17:29.570
a bowl of our homemade
tomato rice soup,

17:29.570 --> 17:31.441
or one of our
daily specials,

17:31.441 --> 17:34.270
you'll always enjoy
the great taste of home.

17:34.270 --> 17:36.664
Each and every meal
starts with a fresh basket

17:36.664 --> 17:39.623
of oven-warmed,
cinnamon-flavored sticky buns.

17:39.623 --> 17:41.277
And don't forget
a slice of apple pie

17:41.277 --> 17:44.150
topped with vanilla ice cream
for dessert.

17:44.150 --> 17:45.977
Founded by Lloyd Miller,

17:45.977 --> 17:47.675
based on recipes passed down

17:47.675 --> 17:49.981
from his
great-great-grandmother,

17:49.981 --> 17:51.722
Miller's would like
to dedicate its menu

17:51.722 --> 17:54.073
to the people
and communities it serves.

18:09.653 --> 18:10.785
That too.

18:10.785 --> 18:11.873
Okay.

18:11.873 --> 18:13.527
