I'll have to check him out.

28:25.225 --> 28:27.227
SARAH:
What about you,
do you ever think about

28:27.227 --> 28:28.358
doing stand-up sometime?

28:28.358 --> 28:29.490
Maybe someday.

28:29.490 --> 28:31.057
