28:51.860 --> 28:56.778
and right away, the bartender
just goes, "Hey, buddy!

28:56.778 --> 28:58.475
We don't serve food here."

28:58.475 --> 29:00.521
[LAUGHING]
[MANDEL LAUGHING]

29:02.610 --> 29:04.568
SARAH:
That's cute.

29:04.568 --> 29:06.788
