asked, but--

33:32.706 --> 33:35.709
I mean, I was gonna go to NASA
and fly spaceships,

33:35.709 --> 33:38.190
but then, you know,
I got the job at Miller's, so...

33:38.190 --> 33:40.801
Oh, yeah, sure.
Couldn't do that.

33:40.801 --> 33:42.933
Heh, heh.
So why the change?

33:42.933 --> 33:46.241
DENNY:
Actually, I was listening
to one of my Lenny Bruce albums,

33:46.241 --> 33:47.677
and on it
he's doing this bit

33:47.677 --> 33:49.853
that I've heard
a thousand times,

33:49.853 --> 33:52.073
