word for word.

33:52.073 --> 33:54.728
And for some reason,
I heard it differently

33:54.728 --> 33:56.686
than any other time
before that.

33:56.686 --> 33:58.253
So I'm at my house,

33:58.253 --> 34:01.604
just...laughing to myself,
and it hit me.

34:01.604 --> 34:03.998
I realized that the reason
it was so different

34:03.998 --> 34:07.349
because what he was saying
was absolutely the truth.

34:07.349 --> 34:10.264
And the truth in itself
is funny.

34:10.264 --> 34:13.485
Heh, heh. And so,
I'm at work the next day,

34:13.485 --> 34:15.574
on my forklift,

34:15.574 --> 34:17.967
and I just start laughing.

34:17.967 --> 34:21.362
