34:30.590 --> 34:32.157
And it hit me,

34:32.157 --> 34:34.855
I hated driving a forklift
for a living.

34:34.855 --> 34:37.553
That's the truth.

34:37.553 --> 34:40.295
You know, and the fact that
it took me 17 years to realize
it

34:40.295 --> 34:43.907
was just...
Heh, it was hysterical.

34:43.907 --> 34:46.214
So you quit.
