34:58.618 --> 35:01.273
I don't mean to laugh,
but it's very funny.

35:01.273 --> 35:04.363
After that, I ended up
applying to the restaurant,

35:04.363 --> 35:06.843
and, you know,
getting the job...

35:06.843 --> 35:08.280
It's been good.

35:08.280 --> 35:10.630
I'm learning a lot
of new things.

35:10.630 --> 35:14.242
Well, good. That's the way
